text: Gallery: STAC golf championship at Cornell University Buy Photo Ryan Johnson of Norwich watches his tee shot fly on number 10 Tuesday during the STAC golf championship at Cornell University's Robert Trent Jones Golf Course. Johnson finished tied for second with a 73. Davis finished tied for second with a 73. Griffiths finished tied for second with a 73. SIMON WHEELER / Staff Photo Fullscreen Buy Photo Alex Hepburn, of Corning, watches his tee shot fly on the 10th hole Tuesday on his way to winning the Southern Tier Athletic Conference golf championship at Cornell University's Robert Trent Jones Golf Course. Hepburn shot an even-par 71 and won by two shots.
